<idea-plugin>
    <id>com.namey</id>
    <name>Namey</name>
    <version>1.0.0</version>
    <vendor email="builtkwon@gmail.com">builtkwon</vendor>
    <description><![CDATA[
        함수 바디를 분석해 AI가 적절한 함수명을 추천해주는 플러그인입니다.<br/>
        <b>Alt+N</b>으로 현재 함수에 대한 이름 3개를 즉시 추천받고, 선택하면 호출부까지 자동 리네임합니다.
    ]]></description>

    <idea-version since-build="232" until-build="241.*"/>

    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.java</depends>
    <depends>org.jetbrains.kotlin</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <applicationService
            serviceImplementation="com.namey.presentation.intellij.NameySettings"/>

        <applicationConfigurable
            parentId="tools"
            instance="com.namey.presentation.intellij.NameyConfigurable"
            id="com.namey.settings"
            displayName="Namey"/>

        <notificationGroup
            id="Namey"
            displayType="BALLOON"
            key="notification.group.namey"/>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <action
            id="com.namey.SuggestNameAction"
            class="com.namey.presentation.intellij.SuggestNameAction"
            text="함수명 추천 (Namey)"
            description="AI를 이용해 현재 함수의 이름을 추천합니다">
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="alt N"/>
            <add-to-group group-id="EditorPopupMenu" anchor="last"/>
        </action>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>
